* gui.mx, gui.my:
  - current cursor position, set at the start of the frame

* gui.lastmx, gui.lastmy:
  - last cursor position, set at the start of the frame


* gui.hotItem:
  - always set to the ID of the item under the cursor
  - reset to 0 at the start of the frame

* activeItem is set to the ID of the item being interacted with



TOOLTIP:

  - drawn at the end of the frame in uiStatePost

